== Overview ==
This module enhances accuracy to a certain degree through the use of a three dimensional prediction grid. Known weak areas on targets are also exploited with this device, giving a higher chance to cause a critical hit.

== Where to Acquire ==
The TC7 Target Predictor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
